      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a reliable and comfortable driving experience. It features a clean interior and a solid mechanical history, making it a perfect choice for anyone looking for a dependable and stylish ride that's ready for many more miles!",
